    "121600280": {
      "title": "A characterization of all the static stabilizing controllers for LTI systems",
      "abstract": "Abstract In this article, we give a complete characterization (geared towards a parametrization) of all the static feedbacks of a given LTI system triplet, in terms of the coefficients of some reduced order Riccati equation, with simultaneously stabilizing solutions and structural constraints – on the coefficients."
